Getting started with Devfolio Builders is simple:Create a Devfolio Profile: Sign up at devfolio.co and build a portfolio showcasing your skills and projects.

Join a Hackathon: Browse upcoming hackathons at https://devfolio.co/hackathons and apply with a single click.

Showcase Your Projects: Upload your projects to the Builders page to gain visibility and attract collaborators.

Nominate a Builder: Recognize a peer’s contributions by nominating them for the Builders page.

Engage with the Community: Join Devfolio’s Telegram group or participate in events like ETHIndia to connect with like-minded innovators.

